nz.govt.natlib.fx

Class CompoundElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • nz.govt.natlib.fx.Element
      • nz.govt.natlib.fx.CompoundElement

  • public class CompoundElement
extends Element
    A type of element which is entirely made up of other elements. When called upon to read a datasource this element calls upon each of it's 'children' to read a part of the datasource. A whole file structure could be parsed using 'trees' of compound elements.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Nic Evans
